Konknni cinem vo Konknni chitrodyom, Bharot chitrodyomachem ek ang zaun asa. Konknni bhaxent pinturam vo chitram Goa, Karnataka, Kerala ani Maharasthra rajyanim toyar zatat. 2013 poryant 45 pinturam riliz zaleant. <ref>http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/entertainment-others/now-showing-konkani-legacy/</ref>

Sorvprothom, [[Mangalore | Koddial]] xohorant aithem zal'lem ''Sukhi Konn'' (1949) pinturak riliz zaum-chem bhag favo zalem na. Tya uprant 1950 vorsant, Portugez xason kallat aithem zal'lelya ''Mogacho Anvddo'' chitrak hem bhag favo zalem. Hea pinturachi riliz ddett zaun asa 24 Oprel. Ani hea karonakch hi tarik monnje 24 Oprelak ''Konknni chitrodyamacho dis'' monn apoitat.

Sukhachem Sopon, Amchem Noxib, Nirmonn, Mhoji Ghorkarn, Kortubancho Sonvsar, Jivit Amchem Oxem, Mog ani Moipas, Bhuierantlo Munis, Suzanne, Boglantt, Padri, Bhogsonne ani Ujwaddu, him thoddim prokhyat chitram zaun asat.

Konknni pintur ''Nachom-ia Kumpasar'' haka khub proxonsa ani puroskar lableat.

